item.title: CVE-2024-1014|2024-08-01T18:26:30.233Z -- se-elektronic%20gmbh -- e-ddc3.3
item.description: Uncontrolled resource consumption vulnerability in SE-elektronic GmbH E-DDC3.3 affecting versions 03.07.03 and higher. An attacker could interrupt the availability of the administration panel by sending multiple ICMP packets.

item.title: CVE-2024-1015|2024-08-01T18:26:30.426Z -- se-elektronic%20gmbh -- e-ddc3.3
item.description: Remote command execution vulnerability in SE-elektronic GmbH E-DDC3.3 affecting versions 03.07.03 and higher. An attacker could send different commands from the operating system to the system via the web configuration functionality of the device.
